title: Temur Partsvania
text:
Temur Partsvania (, , born 6 July 1991) is a <a href="Ukrainians">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for <a href="FC%20Zhetysu">Zhetysu</a> in Kazakhstan. He got Ukrainian citizenship in 2007.
Career.
Desna Chernihiv.
In February 2019 he moved from <a href="Kisv%C3%A1rda%20FC">Kisvárda</a> to <a href="FC%20Desna%20Chernihiv">Desna Chernihiv</a>, the main club in <a href="Chernihiv">Chernihiv</a>, here he played 10 games.
Zhetysu.
In summer 2021 he moved to <a href="FC%20Zhetysu">Zhetysu</a>.
External links.
